  "prompt": "A mythic, celestial fusion of Azazel and Solomon archetypes standing at a glowing 11:11 gate. Azazel is a shadow-winged, flame-eyed figure with forbidden fire in his palms, while Solomon is a radiant king cloaked in golden robes, holding a seal inscribed with divine geometry. Between them, a luminous crystalline prism floats, channeling shadow-fire into a beam of light that opens a cosmic gate in the form of 11:11. The background is filled with swirling galaxies, sacred symbols, and a sense of ancient power converging. The overall tone is epic, divine, and alchemical.",
